{"article_id":"gRqC7PT5vIMM62o5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A second wave of coronavirus cases in the US could be even worse than the first ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"the country 's top health official has warned .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Centers for Disease Control and Prevention","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"( CDC )","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"director Robert Redfield said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"the danger was higher","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"as a fresh outbreak would likely coincide with the flu season .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"It would put `` unimaginable strain '' on the US health care system ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"The US has seen more than 800,000 cases","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"- the highest in the world .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"More than 45,000 people have so far died with coronavirus across the US ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"according to a tally","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"kept by Johns Hopkins University .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"California had its highest one-day rise in new cases on Monday","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"while New Jersey , the worst-hit US state apart from New York , saw its highest increase in deaths in one day .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"President Trump says","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"he will halt applications for US green cards","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"- which give immigrants legal permanent residence and the opportunity","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to apply for American citizenship -","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"for 60 days","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Harvard University says","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"it will keep an $ 8.6m-coronavirus grant","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"despite pressure from President Trump","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"to return it","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"California 's first cases of coronavirus occurred much earlier","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"than previously thought ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"health officials have confirmed .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"A post-mortem examination has revealed","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"that a person","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"who died at home on 6 February in Santa Clara county","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"is now the first known fatality in the US .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Until now , the first fatality was thought to have been a man in Washington state","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"who died on 26 February","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"The US Senate has unanimously approved $ 484bn","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"( £392bn )","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"in coronavirus relief ,","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"including funds","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"designed to help small businesses .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"The legislation will go to the House of Representatives for approval on Thursday","depth":3},{"id":40,"text":"In an interview with the Washington Post , Mr Redfield said","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that `` there 's a possibility","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that the assault of the virus on our nation next winter will actually be even more difficult","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"than the one","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"we just went through '' .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"He urged officials in the US to prepare for the possibility","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"of having to confront a flu and a coronavirus epidemic at the same time .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Mr Redfield stressed the importance","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"of getting flu shots .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"that getting vaccinated `` may allow there to be a hospital bed available for your mother or grandmother","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that may get coronavirus '' .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"The CDC chief said","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"that coronavirus had arrived in the US","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"as the regular flu season was subsiding .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"He argued","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"if it had arrived at the peak of the winter influenza season ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"`` it could have been been really , really , really , really difficult '' .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"His warning comes","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"as several US states are moving to ease lockdown restrictions .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"Mr Redfield said","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that social distancing remained key","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"to curb the spread of the virus","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"and urged officials to keep stressing its importance","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"even as restrictions on movement were lifted .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"He urged state and federal officials to step up tests","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"to identify those","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"who have coronavirus","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"and the people","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"they have had contact .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"that the Centers for Disease Control planned to hire more than 650 people","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"- more than doubling its current staff -","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to help with contact tracing among other things .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"The CDC was also exploring the possibility","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"of using Census Bureau workers","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to help with contact tracing","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"he said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":112,"right":156,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":103,"right":111,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":94,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":87,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":80,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":84,"right":85,"relation":"evaluation"